      "body": "**Run 0010 T12 reconcile (session 0071-horizon-T12): PASS \u2014 FlatteningStratification cone CLOSED and verified.**\n\n- `AlgebraicGeometry.flatLocusStratification_universal` (Nitsure \u00a74, `n=0`) is proved **sorry-free**; `GenericFlatnessGeometric.lean` now sorry-free; proof lives in the new `Picard/FlatteningStratificationUniversal.lean`.\n- **Ground kernel check** (independent): `lake env lean` on the import chain exits `0`; `#print axioms` = `[propext, Classical.choice, Quot.sound]` \u2014 no `sorryAx`.\n- **Math soundness** (fresh work-reviewer): faithful, non-vacuous statement \u2014 finite cover by disjoint immersed strata, per-stratum flatness, and genuine `\u2203!` factorization; the proof cone avoids all 8 live `QuotScheme` sorries.\n- **Blueprint** (fresh blueprint reviewer): `sec:flatstrat_representability` CLEAN \u2014 all 23 `\\lean` pointers resolve, statements match, `\\uses` complete, 0 dangling, reference `nitsure-hilbert-quot` registered.\n- Hygiene: stray `RationalCurveIso.*` scratch files gone; inbox trimmed to 10 memory + 2 info; one stale \"typed sorry\" doc-comment in `QuotScheme.lean` (on the now-proved `pullback_app_isoTensor_baseMap_sectionLinearEquiv`) corrected.\n- `AJC.picrep` remains active: frontier is the 3 `canonicalBaseChangeMap` leaves (gate on `AJC.fbc`) and the 5 headline Quot/Grassmannian reps decls (Route-C coherent-$\\chi$).",
