      "body": "**T12 session 0071: FlatteningStratification cone CLOSED \u2014 `flatLocusStratification_universal` PROVED sorry-free** (axiom-clean [propext, Classical.choice, Quot.sound], full build green 8646 jobs; commits 8b10f96e1a, 3f2342f483; blueprint 3d7d7509d3).\n\nThe theorem moved from `GenericFlatnessGeometric.lean` to the new `AlgebraicJacobian/Picard/FlatteningStratificationUniversal.lean` (~1100 LOC; fully-qualified name preserved, blueprint \\lean pointer unchanged). Stage D: flat constant-rank-e pullbacks kill the strata ideal (`strataData_le_ker`) and factor uniquely through `stratum\u03b9` (IsClosedImmersion.lift); the stratum pullback is flat. Stage E: Nakayama chart supply, `chartLocus`/`rankStratum`/`rankStratum\u03b9` (locally closed, support = rank locus, flat pullback), noetherian rank bound, open rank fibers, disjoint-cofan Sigma assembly + uniqueness through summand ranks. Blueprint: new section sec:flatstrat_representability (22 leanok nodes), universal theorem proof now leanok; AJC 0 dangling.\n\nNew reusable API: `pointRank_pullback` (rank commutes with ANY pullback), `coherentSheafFlat_id_pullback` (flatness stable under arbitrary pullback), `Module.FinitePresentation.exists_matrixPresentation`.\n\n**AJC.picrep frontier now**: (1) 3 canonicalBaseChangeMap leaves in QuotScheme \u2014 flatness-gated on T2/AJC.fbc; (2) the 5 headline Quot/Grassmannian representability decls (Route-C coherent-chi substrate); (3) FGA `instHasPicScheme`. The projective/Hilbert-polynomial upgrade of the stratification returns with the Quot endgame. Updated file-memory `t12-rank-stratum-landed` + coproduct-wall recipes in `v431-instance-wall-recipes-r2`.",
